## Example Configurations

### Using NFS for downloads

```yaml
persistence:
  downloads:
    type: nfs
    nfsServer: your-nfs-server.local
    nfsPath: /mnt/downloads
```

### Using PVC for downloads

```yaml
persistence:
  downloads:
    type: pvc
    storageClassName: your-storage-class
    size: 500Gi
```

